# Global Owners
* @your-org/maintainers

# Infrastructure Code
/infra/ @your-org/devops-team @your-org/platform-team

# GitHub Workflows
/.github/ @your-org/devops-team

# Source Code
/src/ @your-org/developers @your-org/backend-team

# Documentation
*.md @your-org/tech-writers @your-org/maintainers

# Configuration Files
*.yml @your-org/devops-team
*.yaml @your-org/devops-team
*.json @your-org/developers

# Docker Files
Dockerfile @your-org/devops-team @your-org/platform-team
**/Dockerfile @your-org/devops-team @your-org/platform-team

# Terraform Files
*.tf @your-org/devops-team @your-org/platform-team
*.hcl @your-org/devops-team @your-org/platform-team